{"code":200,"msg":"success","data":[{"id":7773,"createTime":"2019-06-25 17:47:50","topicId":null,"tagId":1599,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":1,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">骑跨伤导致尿道断裂时，最有效的治疗方法是</span></span></p><p><br/></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">【解析】</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">男性前尿道损伤中最常见的是尿道球部损伤，骑跨伤是其典型的致病因素。尿道球部裂伤后有排尿困难，但能经尿道顺利插入导尿管者，应保留导尿管引流尿液</span>2</span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\">-</span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\">3周。拔管后适当做尿道扩张。尿道部分裂伤后，如尿道口流血较多、排尿困难、导尿失败、会阴部血肿或尿外渗均应做耻骨上膀胱造瘘。球部尿道撕裂严重或断裂，会阴及阴囊有血肿及尿外渗者，应立即经会阴做尿道端吻合术，并引流血肿及尿外渗。术后应根据排尿情况适当做尿道扩张。</span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">故本题选</span>D。</span></p><p><br/></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":33088,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-25 17:47:50","updateTime":"2019-06-25 17:47:50","isTrue":false,"questionId":7773,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">导尿</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":33089,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-25 17:47:50","updateTime":"2019-06-25 17:47:50","isTrue":false,"questionId":7773,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">耻骨上膀胱造瘘</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":33090,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-25 17:47:50","updateTime":"2019-06-25 17:47:50","isTrue":false,"questionId":7773,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">清除会阴部血肿</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":33091,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-25 17:47:50","updateTime":"2019-06-25 17:47:50","isTrue":true,"questionId":7773,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">经会阴尿道修补</span>